        <body>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="yal.00234.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="yal.00234.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey U S America</name>
                    <date when="1885-01-07" rend="right"><hi rend="underline">Jan. 7 '85</hi><ptr
                            target="yal.00234_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours of Dec. 25 rec'd&#8212;with &#163;1 for books&#8212;I forward them by this
                    mail&#8212;<hi rend="underline">Leaves of Grass</hi> and <hi rend="underline"
                    >Specimen Days</hi>&#8212;two Vols&#8212;</p>
            <p>&#8212;As soon as they reach you safely will
                you kindly send me a card notifying me?<ptr target="yal.00234_n2"/>&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>  
            </closer>

        </body>
